<i> Though most Dayak weapons</i>
<i> doubled as useful tools,</i>

29:39.069 --> 29:41.278
<i> the Pandat was</i>
<i> the only used in war.</i>

29:41.322 --> 29:44.364
<i> Forged from iron, the Pandat</i>
<i> features an angled blade</i>

29:44.408 --> 29:46.784
<i> and could be swung downwards</i>
<i> with two hands.</i>

29:46.827 --> 29:49.244
<i> An iron crosspiece was</i>
<i> inserted through a hole</i>

29:49.288 --> 29:51.872
<i> at the end of the handle,</i>
<i> protecting the user's hands.</i>

29:51.916 --> 29:53.290
<i> The blade was</i>
<i> sometimes decorated</i>

29:53.334 --> 29:55.083
<i> with hair</i>
<i> or rattan plant.</i>

29:55.127 --> 29:57.753
<i> Until the early 20th century,</i>
<i> Dayak raiders</i>

29:57.797 --> 29:59.755
<i> plundered coastal settlements</i>
<i> for resources,</i>

29:59.799 --> 30:01.965
<i> money,</i>
<i> and even enemy heads,</i>

30:02.009 --> 30:05.052
<i> proving just how deadly</i>
<i> this weapon could be.</i>

30:05.095 --> 30:06.595
You will have five days
at your home forge

30:06.639 --> 30:08.263
to complete
this challenge.

30:08.307 --> 30:10.265
At the end of five days,
you will return

30:10.309 --> 30:13.352
and present your Pandats
to our panel of expert judges.

30:13.395 --> 30:15.103
Only after they've
subjected those

30:15.147 --> 30:18.857
to some excruciating punishment
in our weapons tests

30:18.901 --> 30:21.318
will they declare one of you
the "Forged in Fire" champion

30:21.362 --> 30:24.404
who also walks away
with a check for ten grand.

30:24.448 --> 30:26.448
Good luck, bladesmiths.
We'll see you in five days.

30:26.492 --> 30:32.329
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

30:32.373 --> 30:35.791
<i> - It's day one, and we are</i>
<i> at my blacksmith club,</i>

30:35.835 --> 30:38.001
Southern Ohio
Forge and Anvil.

30:38.045 --> 30:41.004
<i> I would like to have</i>
<i> my blade and the handle</i>

30:41.048 --> 30:43.215
<i> forged to width</i>
<i> and thickness.</i>

30:43.259 --> 30:45.425
If I get that part of it
done today,

30:45.469 --> 30:48.595
<i> it'll just really</i>
<i> boost my confidence</i>

30:48.639 --> 30:51.056
that we've started off
on the right foot

30:51.100 --> 30:53.350
