31:43.110 --> 31:46.194
I mean, this is--
this is kind of intense.

31:46.238 --> 31:47.154
Oh, [bleep], okay.

31:47.197 --> 31:48.780
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

31:48.824 --> 31:51.992
Oh, [bleep], okay.
Yeah, boys.

31:52.036 --> 31:53.160
Damn it!

