33:06.068 --> 33:08.652
so it won't get soft.

33:08.696 --> 33:10.821
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

33:10.864 --> 33:12.864
<i> I've really been fighting</i>
<i> the wind with it.</i>

33:12.908 --> 33:17.327
<i> About as fast as you get it</i>
<i> warmed up, it cools down.</i>

33:17.371 --> 33:19.621
<i> I also have to keep</i>
<i> water in the trench,</i>

33:19.665 --> 33:22.040
<i> and when you've got</i>
<i> a very hot torch</i>

33:22.084 --> 33:25.919
