33:25.963 --> 33:27.754
<i> I'm not sure</i>
<i> I'm gonna get it done.</i>

33:27.798 --> 33:29.965
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

33:30.009 --> 33:31.925
<i> - Day four,</i>
<i> either we top the hill</i>

33:31.969 --> 33:33.635
or we roll down
